timeline.bodyText: Why not use Math.pow() method instead of implementing own power method?
timeline.author: srnagar

replies.bodyText:
Yeah, we can use Math.pow(),
unless @mikeharder had any concerns that this might create any performance impact or inconsistencies across languages.
replies.author: g2vinay

replies.bodyText: I was afraid of the conversion between double and int.  But if you know this is safe you can replace with Math.pow().
replies.author: mikeharder

replies.bodyText: Math.pow() works for this usecase, we can replace it
replies.author: srnagar
